metadata.name: EMBLEM 1/42
metadata.description:
This token is a fraction of MARK'S roundtable emblem: a composition of each address engraved on the 42 sets of rings claimed by collectors of MARK. This unifying insignia incites equalitarian discourse amongst its members. The emblem is the coat of arms of this alliance.

ADDRESS: 0x11111AAca47680083F80E6be026439CeA762e954  
ENS: ring1.eth
